n screwing with this thing? Your questions have become more redundant and annoying than the last three \"Highlander\" movies.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">I\'ve had it with this school, Skinner. Low test scores, class after class of ugly, ugly childrenâ€¦ And here I am using my own lungs like a sucker. Oh, I\'m in no condition to drive. Wait a minute. I don\'t have to listen to myself. I\'m drunk.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Kids, you tried your best and you failed miserably. The lesson is, never try. I was saying \"Boo-urns.\" Don\'t kid yourself, Jimmy. If a cow ever got the chance, he\'d eat you and everyone you care about!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Your guilty consciences may make you vote Democratic, but secretly you all yearn for a Republican president to lower taxes, brutalize criminals, and rule you like a king! I\'ve done everything the Bible says â€” even the stuff that contradicts the other stuff!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Slow down, Bart! My legs don\'t know how to be as long as yours. Donuts. Is there anything they can\'t do? I was saying \"Boo-urns.\" I don\'t like being outdoors, Smithers. For one thing, there\'s too many fat children.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue