l be back. You can\'t keep the Democrats out of the White House forever, and when they get in, I\'m back on the streets, with all my criminal buddies.</li><li style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 1em; line-height: 1.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">Oh, so they have Internet on computers now!</li></ul><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Well, he\'s kind of had it in for me ever since I accidentally ran over his dog. Actually, replace \"accidentally\" with \"repeatedly\" and replace \"dog\" with \"son.\" I\'ve had it with this school, Skinner. Low test scores, class after class of ugly, ugly childrenâ€¦</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Here\'s to alcohol, the cause of â€” and solution to â€” all life\'s problems. You don\'t like your job, you don\'t strike. You go in every day and do it really half-assed. That\'s the American way.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Kids, we need to talk for a moment about Krusty Brand Chew Goo Gum Like Substance. We all knew it contained spider eggs, but the hantavirus? That came out of left field. So if you\'re experiencing numbness and/or comas, send five dollars to antidote, PO boxâ€¦ We started out like Romeo and Juliet, but it ended up in tragedy.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Brace yourselves gentlemen. According to the gas chromatograph, the secret ingredient isâ€¦ Love!? Who\'s been screwing with this thing? Your questions have become more redundant and annoying than the last three \"Highlander\" movies.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">I\'ve had it with this school, Skinner. Low test scores, class after class of ugly, ugly childrenâ€¦ And here I am using my own lungs like a sucker. Oh, I\'m in no condition to drive. Wait a minute. I don\'t have to listen to myself. I\'m drunk.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Kids, you tried your best and you failed miserably. The lesson is, never try. I was saying \"Boo-urns.\" Don\'t kid yourself, Jimmy. If a cow ever got the chance, he\'d eat you and everyone you care about!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Your guilty consciences may make you vote Democratic, but secretly you all yearn for a Republican president to lower taxes, brutalize criminals, and rule you like a king! I\'ve done everything the Bible says â€” even the stuff that contradicts the other stuff!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Slow down, Bart! My legs don\'t know how to be as long as yours. Donuts. Is there anything they can\'t do? I was saying \"Boo-urns.\" I don\'t like being outdoors, Smithers. For one thing, there\'s too many fat children.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">And now, in the spirit of the season: start shopping. And for every dollar of Krusty merchandise you buy, I will be nice to a sick kid. For legal purposes, sick kids may include hookers with a cold. I hope this has taught you kids a lesson: kids never learn.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">I can\'t go to juvie. They use guys like me as currency. Look out, Itchy! He\'s Irish! Homer no function beer well without. I\'ve done everything the Bible says â€” even the stuff that contradicts the other stuff!</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: Roboto, \" helvetica=\"\" neue\",=\"\" sans-serif;=\"\" font-size:=\"\" 16px;\"=\"\">Brace yourselves gentlemen. According to the gas chromatograph, the secret ingredient isâ€¦ Love!? Who\'s been screwing with this thing? He didn\'t give you gay, did he? Did he?! I can\'t go to juvie. They use guys like me as currency.</p>', 'a', 6, '2018-05-09 16:51:52', '2018-05-10 16:12:01'),
